## What You Get

This boilerplate includes everything you need to run a professional blog:

- **Blazing fast performance** - Astro ships zero JavaScript by default
- **Visual CMS** - Edit content through a friendly interface at `/keystatic`
- **SEO optimized** - Meta tags, Open Graph, structured data built-in
- **LLM discoverable** - AI crawlers can easily understand your content
- **Categories & Tags** - Organize your posts with taxonomy
- **Responsive design** - Looks great on all devices

## How to Use Keystatic

To create or edit content:

1. Run `npm run dev` to start your development server
1. Visit `http://localhost:4321/keystatic` in your browser
1. Create new posts, categories, or tags using the visual editor
1. Your changes are saved automatically to your project files

## Customizing Your Site

### Change Site Information

Update `astro.config.mjs` to set your production URL:

```javascript
export default defineConfig({
  site: 'https://yourdomain.com',
  // ...
});
```

### Customize Colors

Edit `tailwind.config.mjs` to change your brand colors:

```javascript
colors: {
  primary: {
    500: '#your-color-here',
    // ...
  },
}
```

### Update Site Name

Edit `keystatic.config.ts` to change the CMS brand name, and update the components to show your site name.

## SEO Features

Every blog post automatically gets:

- **Meta description** from your post description
- **Open Graph tags** for social media sharing
- **JSON-LD structured data** for search engines
- **Canonical URLs** to prevent duplicate content
- **Sitemap** generated automatically

## LLM Discovery

This site is optimized for AI discovery with:

- Clean semantic HTML structure
- `/llms.txt` file describing the site for AI crawlers
- Explicit permissions for AI crawlers in `robots.txt`
- Structured data helping AI understand content context

